reviewText: this is an awesome collection of music videos by many bands, such as: dimmu borgir, immortal, behemoth, blind guardian, accept, death angel, nightwish etc. it also has bonus clips and live clips as well. the only problem i have is that i should have MORE. well, i have there is a vol. 2 because i am getting that as well. fans of metal and rock genres, this is a must have. for some, you may not like. but for true fans, A MUST HAVE.
